            <title>[LU-17112] kernel update [RHEL7.9 3.10.0-1160.99.1.el7]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17112</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: cls_flower: out-of-bounds write in fl_set_geneve_opt() (CVE-2023-35788)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;hw: amd: Cross-Process Information Leak (CVE-2023-20593)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Bug Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;nf_conntrack causing nfs to stall (BZ#2128262)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Request to backport upstream commit 5e2d2cc2588b, 26a8b12747c9, and e98fa02c4f2e for RHEL 7.9.z (BZ#2180681)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fix soft lockup happens in gfs2_dir_get_hash_table() (BZ#2190450)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2023:4819&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2023:4819&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
